basics.summary: I am currently a student at the university of Canberra, studying a bachelor of information technology. I have extensive knowledge of current computing technologies with a particular focus on web development trends, and have used these skills in the deployment of a Canberra based architect's web presence through a web development internship, as well as working on multiple personal and academic projects. My aim is to further develop these skills, gaining additional professional experience in web design, in order to pursue my career goals in the it industry.
